# IBM - stepzen
1. Copy Login command for the CLI from https://eu-central-a.dashboard.ibm.stepzen.com/
2. create and go to stepzen folder
3. run command: stepzen init
4. run command: stepzen import postgresql
5. Provide our db details
6. run command: stepzen start

------------------------
If we have the endpoint and the stepzen folder, to run the stepzen we should use this command inside the stepzen folder: stepzen start
If we need to be logged in, we should first run the 1st step